;https://www.theverge.com/23656561/sonos-era-100-speaker-review-features&quot; >;&lt;strong>;Sonos Era 100&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;&lt;strong>;智能扬声器&lt;/strong>;用作&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type的后环绕声/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/ultimate-immersive-set-arc-sub-era-300-pair&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;2,211 美元（折扣 385 美元）&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en -us/shop/premium-immersive-set-arc-sub-era-100-pair&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;分别为 1,856 美元（折扣 340 美元）&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;r2z8Jk&quot;>;如果您需要复习一下，Sonos...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934836/ sonos-arc-beam-ray-era-300-soundbars-smart-speakers&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934836/sonos-arc-beam-ray-era-300-soundbars-smart-speakers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23934836/sonos-arc-beam-ray-era-300-soundbars-smart-speakers</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-27T12:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-27T12:00:00-04:00</updated><title>历经两季，苹果科幻剧《入侵》终于重磅推出</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple TV Plus 系列入侵第 2 季中 Shioli Kutsuna 的剧照。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4e4d_FD8yTYBea5la6rXLAOxf4k=/0x0:6240x4160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72800478/Invasion_Photo_021005.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Shioli Kutsuna 饰演 Mitsuki。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZfReym&quot;>;在《入侵》前两季的大部分时间里，该剧的角色似乎彼此独立移动。很明显，他们正朝着相似的方向前进，路径会以某种方式汇合，但直到第二季结局&lt;em>;入侵&lt;/em>;才最终开始走到一起。这也为这部剧在未来的一场大决战做好了准备。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TVkXyY&quot;>;&lt;em>;入侵&lt;/em>;的剧情很像一部由角色驱动的戏剧，而恰好被设置在外星人入侵的地面。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22740520/invasion-review-apple-tv-plus&quot;>;开始时&lt;em>;缓慢&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; - &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2021/11/12/22776188/invasion-apple-tv-plus-episode-6-alien&quot;>;我们甚至没有看到这些尖尖的、斑点状的入侵者，直到几个小时&lt;/a>; 中的剧集 - 并且基本上保持这种状态，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23833132/invasion-season-2-review-apple-tv-plus&quot;>;尽管第二季逐渐恶化稍微提高强度开始&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;v9kMDo&quot;>;&lt;em>;这个故事包含剧透...&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23932047 /invasion-season-2-review-apple-tv-plus&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23932047/invasion-season-2-review-apple-tv-plus" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23932047/invasion-season-2-review-apple-tv-plus</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry></feed>